Taint Blood

An evil ritual which calls upon the dark totemic
spirits of nature.  After casting this spell, a
druid need only touch his target to send a
virulent poison through its blood.  Armor is no
help, and the poison will continue to do damage
beyond its initial amount, should the victim
survive.

Command: taint <target> (defaults to attacker)
Base Cost: 90 SP
Base Recovery: medium
Base Effect: damage (moderate, continuing)
Base Duration: long
Guild Level: 11
